    <p>Goli Probiotic+ is the only product in our digestion guide that combines all three pillars of gut health — probiotic, prebiotic, and postbiotic — into a single gummy supplement. The innovation lies in understanding what each component does: the probiotic Bacillus subtilis DE111 is a spore-forming strain that naturally withstands stomach acid, heat, and manufacturing processes in its dormant endospore form, delivering near-100% of its organisms alive to the intestine. The prebiotic XOS (xylo-oligosaccharides) selectively feeds beneficial Bifidobacteria and Lactobacilli without promoting harmful bacterial growth — acting as targeted fuel for the good bacteria already in your gut. The postbiotic MCC1849 — a heat-stable preparation of Lactobacillus paracasei — provides immune-modulating metabolites that function regardless of bacterial viability, making it inherently shelf-stable and independent of the survival challenges that affect live probiotics.</p>

